{"tid":286311,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"廚師偷名牌鞋自瀆 女事主損失4.3萬","createTime":"2017-06-16T13:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T14:44:14.000Z","uid":3806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0336cfea7beac697475a87b4eb1358cb6a8b7f4a","tid":286311,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:25:19.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】居於馬灣村屋的25歲女子，常將名貴高跟鞋放在屋外鞋櫃，數月間先後發現5對總值4.3萬元的鞋不翼而飛，其中一對更是Valentino高跟鞋。她和家人遂加裝大閘和閉路電視，發現鞋癡出沒，最終鄰居發現鞋癡於附近徘徊而報警。鞋癡承認偷鞋以供他自瀆，完事後將鞋棄掉。<br />\n<br />\n包括Valentino高跟鞋<br />\n在工廠食堂任職廚師兼且是太子爺的被告顏志軒（26歲）昨在區院承認4項爆竊罪，指他去年1至8月期間，四度在事主的住所梯間偷走5對女裝鞋。辯方求情表示，被告已預備支票賠償予事主。法官要求索取被告的心理、精神、社會服務令及感化報告，押後判刑至7月11日，其間准被告擔保。<br />\n案情指事主陳靉彤前年12月發現紅色Valentino高跟鞋失蹤，她不以為然，但3個月後再有4對鞋不見了，她認定有人偷鞋，遂於公用梯間安裝閉路電視。至去年3月20日晚，陳聽到屋外狗吠，開門赫然發現被告站在鞋櫃，被告即時逃跑，陳因太驚沒追上前。閉路電視拍到被告曾搜索鞋櫃，家人決定在梯間安裝大閘。<br />\n至8月7日晚上，鄰居發現被告形迹可疑，並伸手試圖打開梯間大閘，鄰居即上前攔截及報警。被告被捕後承認偷鞋用來自瀆，3月時兩度上門搜鞋櫃，但因沒發現心儀鞋款故沒犯案，而他去年初所偷的鞋已扔掉。<br />\n案件編號：DCCC91/17<br />\n■記者黃幗慧、歐陽聯發"},{"pid":"5261b4644841da920aeec00314c954bc5f017900","tid":286311,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:25:52.000Z","msg":"皮鞋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0e382b781fb4ed2f75e6c969a028704d78f4a3","tid":286311,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:27:02.000Z","msg":"皮鞋點自瀆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d03e150b73c3b017a3dc44c95f6c9c84834166","tid":286311,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:29:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/8/7244/7186681137_ae906fcf0e_b.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F8%2F7244%2F7186681137_ae906fcf0e_b.jpg&d=6SNwFKqVviYZE5habXOENcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=68536af2\" target=\"_blank\">https://c2.staticflickr.com/8/7244/7186681137_ae906fcf0e_b.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79ae14bdf9083a305fb075a0b55ff49c001eb88","tid":286311,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皮鞋點自瀆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n劣𨶙"},{"pid":"783b9c070cea69fa3176a6944e7f00dec1a20fe2","tid":286311,"uid":28737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"陳<span style=\"color: red;\">靉</span>彤<br />\n罰抄點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d536149c37b5d0c6a98a0d1bd0aa61de983bb3","tid":286311,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳<span style=\"color: red;\">靉</span>彤<br />\n罰抄點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陳雲愛彤"},{"pid":"4c94a70752acdefc560077d54d6d7e57e60218ed","tid":286311,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>陳<span style=\"color: red;\">靉</span>彤<br />\n罰抄點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陳雲愛彤</blockquote><br />\n個字點讀"},{"pid":"b33894e8a7274a4a5e7dfab4e656fbadc9d82252","tid":286311,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:21:25.000Z","msg":"奇雲道爾（26歲）"},{"pid":"0e48cc5bf948c35948939b87507372f377dfc709","tid":286311,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:26:29.000Z","msg":"我識佢 佢有上開連登 名就唔開<br />\n不過個名有一個😍符號"},{"pid":"43c2d4330dc46642582b4c1edaac123a63b71870","tid":286311,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bff68339522ed26786d1f9a2ebf15